
DOM : Document Object Model
    => DOM gives a Structural representation of HTML elements
    => HTML is parsed and converted into DOM 
    => The structural representation will be the tree structure 

DOM Manipulation 
    => Manipulating HTML elements / tags from Javascript is DOM 
    => To support dynamic operation 
    => To perform operations in HTML elements we are using DOM Manipulation 


